      "span_text": "The accuracy and validity of this method were reported in previous studies, showing a good to excellent test-retest reliability.    There are two different forms of MND: simple and complex MND. This classification is based on the number of dysfunctions present (before the onset of puberty) or on the type of dysfunction (after the onset of puberty)."
